        <date>1943</date>
      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The still from the feature film ‘O noapte furtunoasă’ (A stormy night) shows a young man, a woman and an elderly man in a room. The elderly man has a stick in his right hand and has his left hand around the young man’s head with his left hand. The woman appears to intervene.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The feature was directed by Jean Georgescu and was released in 1943.</ab>
